@X0E  Help is available on the following Join Conference topics:@X03

       @X09[@X0E+@X09]@X03 Plus      @X09[@X0EA@X09]@X03 Abandon   @X09[@X0EN@X09]@X03 New
       @X09[@X0E-@X09]@X03 Minus     @X09[@X0EL@X09]@X03 Locate    @X09[@X0ES@X09]@X03 Status
       @X09[@X0E#@X09]@X03 Number    @X09[@X0EM@X09]@X03 Main      @X09[@X0EY@X09]@X03 Your
    
           @X09[@X0ESummary@X09]@X03     @X09[@X0EExamples@X09]@X03

Enter text inside the Square Brackets ie: M for help on MAIN



